features: Low Profile Video Card: Merely 5.7" in length, 0.71" thickness, takes 1 slot, gives it an additional advantage to fit in slimmer or SFF PC cases . You can get it for use in regular ATX cases to have more room inside your cabinet for better airflow.

Great Value Video Card: Based on the Lexa /Polaris GPU architecture and comes with 512 CUDA Cores, 4GB GDDR5 memory and 128-bit bus width, great choice for users, who want to upgrade from integrated graphics or upgrade from older graphics cards.

Dual-Monitor Display: Equipped with DP 1.4 HDMI 2.0 ports, good for 4K (@60Hz via HDMI) or 8K (@60Hz via DP) display and video playback while connecting 2 monitors simultaneously, give you more screen real estate, increasing your productivity.

PCI-e Bus Powered: Powered entirely by the PCIe 3.0 bus,compatible x8 x16, no require any additional power connectors, allows you plug and play, easy to use. Thanks for its low profile design, its max power consumption is up to 55W.

OS Support: SRhonyra RX 550 low profile video card works well with Windows 11/Windows 10/Windows 8.1/Windows 8/Windows 7/Linux (32/64 bit), and Linux 32 bit RAM, Linux arrch64, Solaris ×86/×64 and FreeBSD ×86/×64. Feel free to contact us for any questions.

Single-slot width This DP+HDMI dual outputs graphics card comes with a half-height bracket, fits your small form factor system well. An full-helight bracket also included in the package. Dual-monitor graphics card Support for up to dual Displays: HDMI 4K resolutions 3840×2160 @60Hz ; Display Port 8K resolution 7680×4320 @60Hz. Energy Efficient This mutli-screen video card requires only 55 watts of power from the PCIe 3.0 x8 x16 bus. Recommended 350 watt or greater power supply. 2 Audio Outputs This discrete Displayport & HDMI outputs graphcis card support 2 channel audio out via cable. Please change the setting for the playback device enable HDMI & DP audio output.

How multiple monitors system can benefit your business In a digital-first world, everything lives on the screen. It is hard to try to jump between windows to get work done efficiently. For a personal user, the multiple monitors setup will boost your productivity, saving your time and energe, as you will have plenty of screen real estate, no need to reduce the window sizes to show more on the single screen, no more often tabbing back and forth between windows. For enterprised users, the system will ensure your business stands out from the crowd. Featuring editable display, you could use it to show your latest products and services and inform potential buyers about the inventory available. Connect up to 2 displays with support for resolutions up to 4K resolution, you could not only use it for a video wall, restaurant signage, but also a home theater setups, and welcome monitors. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 5, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sorprendido por buen desempeño
reviews.reviewText: Necesitaba una tarjeta de video para un pc SFF algo antiguo pero con buen procesador y buena RAM (C7 6700 y 16 G de RAM) . Esta tarjeta me sorpendió por el desempeño con juegos sin ajustar parámetros (fluye bien con juegos no muy exigentes). Y si ajustas parámetros (bajas resolución y eliminas algunos efectos) corren bien todos los juegos.
